==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: fuzee
<hw>fuzee</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>a friction match with a
large head that will stay alight in the wind.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> fusee.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>any device by which an explosive charge is
ignited.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> fuse, fuze, fusee, primer.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fuzz</ent>⟦br⟧
